{"_path":"/2025/05/lxgw-wenkai-web","_dir":"05","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"更换网站字体为霞鹜文楷屏幕阅读版（LXGW WenKai Screen）","description":"本文介绍了如何更换全局网站字体为霞鹭文楷（LXGW WenKai）及其屏幕阅读版（LXGW WenKai Screen）","date":"2025-05-28T10:24:26.000Z","categories":["技术探索"],"tags":["Web","Fonts"],"image":"https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/Web/WenKai-Demo.webp","readingTime":{"text":"4 min read","minutes":3.69,"time":221400,"words":738},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"前言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"霞鹭文楷一直是我很喜欢的中文开源字体，我在我的电脑上全局都使用了它的屏幕阅读版。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最近打算在博客上也全局使用它，简单记录下我的更换流程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2020 年 12 月，日本著名字体厂商 FONTWORKS 在 GitHub 上发布了 7 款日文字体，分别为 Train、Klee、Stick、Rock-n-Roll、Reggae、Rampart 和 DotGothic16，根据 SIL Open Font License 1.1 授权许可开源。7 款开源日文字体各有各的特点，而这 7 款字体中，字符数量最多的是 Klee。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这是一款有着日本教科书体风格的字体，兼有仿宋和楷体的特点。一些 DIY 字体爱好者曾先后用仿宋等字体补全这款字体，作为手机系统的美化字体移植在 iOS、Android 等手机系统中，受到很多玩机发烧友的欢迎。不过这样补全的字体有一些不足之处。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第一，原有字体和后补字体之间有着一定的差异，致使一些不同的文字（如 Klee 原有汉字与后补简体字）混排之后会有一定的违和感。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二，由于补字所用的字体为商业版权字体，补全之后不可用于商业用途，还会有侵权的风险。此外，目前现有的开源中文字库里，楷体类寥寥无几，仿宋类则几乎没有。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"鉴于此，也为了丰富开源中文字体中的楷体门类，2021 年 1 月 20 日起， LXGW 开始了为 Klee One 这一高质量的日文开源字体补全简繁常用字的尝试。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"因该字体具有一定的「文艺气息」，命名 「霞鹜文楷」（其实当初是感觉这款字体适合正文阅读定名「文楷」，后来发现这款字体可能并不太适合大段正文排版，相比之下更加适合诗词之类的中等长度文本排版，或者注释排版）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由于 Klee One 字体的 Regular 字重太细不太适合阅读，选取原字体 SemiBold 字重作为 Regular 字重。经过长时间的积累，目前已发展成简繁日韩均支持的 3 字重字体家族 （虽然拙劣粗糙了点） 。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"引入"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引入"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在网页的"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<head>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"标签内适当位置引入字体 CSS。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你可以选择屏幕阅读优化版或者其他版本。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"alert","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此处使用了"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.zstatic.net/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zstatic CDN"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，你可以自由更换为其他"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CDNJS"}]},{"type":"text","value":"的 CDN，但请注意不要选择被投毒的其他几款 CDN。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"pre","props":{"className":"language-javascript shiki shiki-themes catppuccin-latte one-dark-pro","code":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://s4.zstatic.net/ajax/libs/lxgw-wenkai-screen-webfont/1.7.0/style.min.css\" />\n","language":"javascript","meta":"","style":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"__ignoreMap":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"class":"line","line":1},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-default:#179299;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-default:#1E66F5;--shiki-dark:#E06C75"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"link"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{"style":"--shiki-default:#DF8E1D;--shiki-default-font-style:inherit;--shiki-dark:#D19A66;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic"},"children":[{"typ